  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience some of the world's most amazing natural wonders as fully 3D immersive environments! Stand in breathtaking views of <strong>towering mountains, majestic canyons, flowing waterfalls, sweeping deserts, serene beaches, and iconic national parks</strong> - meticulously 3D captured to truly immerse you. Feel like you're really there as BRINK Traveler brings these beautiful sights to you today! 🌄</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462520/extras/7efc774641abe7a423b1f3b38c5346ae.poster.avif?t=1734624730\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462520/extras/7efc774641abe7a423b1f3b38c5346ae.webm?t=1734624730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462520/extras/7efc774641abe7a423b1f3b38c5346ae.mp4?t=1734624730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏞️ Featuring:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >48 incredible 3D immersive environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A few meters of room-scale walkable area in each location</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel solo or with friends & family in multiplayer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Virtual Guide & AI Travel Assistant to learn about locations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy 2D apps (browser, videos, gaming) within environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot photos to save or share with friends</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Download or delete locations at will (~500MB each)</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New locations & features added regularly!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462520/extras/5afc5b9ef6208eb206d2ddfcb1639808.poster.avif?t=1734624730\" width=600 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462520/extras/5afc5b9ef6208eb206d2ddfcb1639808.webm?t=1734624730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462520/extras/5afc5b9ef6208eb206d2ddfcb1639808.mp4?t=1734624730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🗺️ Location Highlights:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pulpit Rock NO, Horseshoe Bend US, Navagio Beach GR, Landmannalaugar IS, Arches National Park US, Aoraki / Mt Cook NZ, Cappadocia TR, Ulsanbawi KR, Antelope Canyon US, Mt Sunday NZ, White Pocket US, Cirque de Gavarnie FR, Death Valley National Park US, Peña Ezkaurre SP, Bryce Canyon National Park US, Pilat Dune FR, Mount Whitney US, Haifoss IS, and many more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462520/extras/eeeca7a774e285f2a02c3c30609cce66.poster.avif?t=1734624730\" width=600 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462520/extras/eeeca7a774e285f2a02c3c30609cce66.webm?t=1734624730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462520/extras/eeeca7a774e285f2a02c3c30609cce66.mp4?t=1734624730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌎 Supporting Nature:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1% of every sale is donated to environmental charity partners dedicated to protecting these wonderful places of the world for future generations!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462520/extras/9ebf2acfbcef77e105eef21f1f90f55f.avif?t=1734624730\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p>",
